title: S3 Ep112: National News: Reba Was A Man Edition - Hr.1
itunes:title: National News: Reba Was A Man Edition - Hr.1
description: Book Critic, Susan Cummins reviews the new Peter James Autobiography, "Heaven, Can You Hear Me" By Gian Temperelli.  Guest National Correspondent, Michelle Fox has an interesting story about country star Reba McEntyre and her belief that she was a man in a past life, among other news stories this week! and Tech Talk correspondent Bill Murphy welcomes in guest Mike Colletta to talk ITC!
